4. Potential passive income from $APE. 

In short, future improvements in tech that would give the average Joe greater access to bigger ticket, blue chip NFTs + access to more liquidity options in the future as the holder make it a tough call to sell now.

1. Increased adoption of https://t.co/I0pCGi0GmE and other fractionalization products that make it easy to get ape exposure without buying one in full.

2. Maturation of DAOs/creation of more DAOs. Similar concept to fractionalization.

3. Maturation of NFT lending products.
If you believe apes are the premier NFT brand, there are reasons to be bullish on where things can go even as we approach pretty lofty levels‚Ä¶.üëá
